1) install node js
2) check if node js is installed
    node -v       <- this provides the installed nodejs version
3) check if npm is installed
    npm -v        <- this provides the installed npm version
4) Configure repository if required
    npm config set registry <repository URL with port>
5) install typeScript
    npm install -g typeScript
    typeScript get downloaded in the below folder with a folder named typeScript
    C:\Users\username\AppData\Roaming\npm\node_modules\
6) Check if typeScript is properly installed
    tsc -v         <- this provides the installed typeScript version
